WEBVTT

00:04.569 --> 00:06.484
- Previously on
"The Arrangement"...

00:06.528 --> 00:09.705
- This is your lead actor.
This is your star.

00:09.748 --> 00:11.489
I thought it was more important
to focus on directing,

00:11.533 --> 00:13.143
and let Megan carry the film.

00:13.187 --> 00:14.449
- And you... you honestly
think she can do that?

00:14.492 --> 00:16.059
- Oh, Megan's gonna
blow everybody away.

00:16.103 --> 00:17.669
- I said don't look at me!

00:17.713 --> 00:20.542
- If you stay, we're talking
about a full-blown affair.

00:20.585 --> 00:22.152
- Yeah.

00:22.196 --> 00:25.329
- Please welcome
the incredible Xavier Hughes!

00:25.373 --> 00:27.418
- That's my boyfriend.

00:27.462 --> 00:29.072
- Have you ever acted before?

00:30.682 --> 00:32.293
- I need you,

00:32.336 --> 00:34.817
'cause I'm gonna burn
the whole thing down.

00:34.860 --> 00:36.340
- It's not just stress.
- Are you okay?

00:36.384 --> 00:37.559
- My stomach.

00:37.602 --> 00:39.169
- Something else is going on,

00:39.213 --> 00:40.431
and I think you and I
should work together

00:40.475 --> 00:42.172
until we figure out what it is.

